vi index.html

```
<h1>Tomcat has been containerized successfully</h1>

This is a custom page
```

vi Dockerfile

```
FROM tomcat

COPY index.html /usr/local/tomcat/webapps/sample/
```

docker build -t custom-tom .
docker login

Username:
Password:

docker push sreedevijun92/tomcat:2
vi custom-tom.yml

```
apiVersion: apps/v1beta2
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: custom-tomcat
spec:
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: tomcat
  replicas: 1
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: tomcat
    spec:
      containers:
        - name: tomcat-cntr
          image: sreedevijun92/tomcat:2
          ports:
            - containerPort: 8080
              protocol: TCP
```




